 the long term because its presence means we can take long term contrarian investments that by their very nature are out of favor and disliked when we buy them  your trust helps avoid emotional reactions that lead to poor returns  our goal is to succeed by making you money over the long term in as safe a way as possible  we want to earn your trust by managing your money intelligently explaining what we are doing and being responsive to your needs   contact us about us about grisanti history our team contact us large cap value portfolio philosophy  process past quarterly letters high income equity portfolio philosophy  process past quarterly letters in the news grisanti videos articles  third avenue suite c new york ny   copyright   grisanti capital management llc all rights reserved site map      web design and domain names by contact us  grisanti capital management search for home about us about grisanti history our team large cap value portfolio philosophy  process past quarterly letters high income equity portfolio philosophy  process past quarterly letters in the news articles videos bloomberg large cap value commentary st quarter  continue reading high income equity portfolio commentary st quarter  continue reading contact us to learn more about our large cap value portfolio and high income equity portfolio contact us grisanti capital management  third avenue suite c new york ny   infogrisanticom grisanti capital management proudly serves clients in new york city and beyond about us about grisanti history our team contact us large cap value portfolio philosophy  process past quarterly letters high income equity portfolio philosophy  process past quarterly letters in the news grisanti videos articles  third avenue suite c new york ny   copyright   grisanti capital management llc all rights reserved site map      web design and domain names by our history  new york city  grisanti capital management search for home about us about grisanti history our team large ca